	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, such a thing is possible. One homebrew game I have seen uses both controllers together for a single-player game, but I don't know if it is what you meant or not. What exactly is it you want to do? Can you perhaps give an example?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
