	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Dian Shi Mali (the &quot;PUSH START TO RICH&quot; slot machine game) puts some bet buttons and the start button on the second controller because there aren't enough buttons on the first.<br /><br />Smash TV rotates both controllers 90 degrees to the right into the &quot;double fisted&quot; position, so that one Control Pad moves and the other fires.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
